# Cloudflare Pages — HTTP response headers (copied to dist/_headers at build).
# Advertise agent resources via RFC 8288 Link headers. Only verified, existing
# targets are listed (llms.txt, sitemap, RSS) — a dead Link is worse than none.
# Vary: Accept on every response so caches never serve HTML to a later
# `Accept: text/markdown` request (negotiation cache-poisoning guard).
/*
  Link: </llms.txt>; rel="llms-txt"; type="text/plain", </sitemap-index.xml>; rel="sitemap"; type="application/xml", </rss.xml>; rel="alternate"; type="application/rss+xml"
  Vary: Accept
